        "created_at": "2020-08-01T13:15:38.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Yes, 2009 has been released this year, before the 2008. It\u2019s really excellent, with serious structure for the long haul.</p>\n<p>Beyond Dom P\u00e9rignon, a number of other producers released 2009 before 2009, such as Egly-Ouriet for example. Makes a lot of sense.</p>",
